    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The engine starts up immediately and runs smoothly, and the transmission provides consistent, predictable shifts. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of regular use, there are no major defects or mechanical issues to report. It is a dependable driver that is ready for the road.",
