    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic work to be made roadworthy again. The engine has significant leaks and runs roughly, while the transmission shifts harshly. Externally, the car suffers from widespread paint peeling, deep scratches, and several large dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components are currently non-functional. It is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for a dedicated project or as a parts donor.",
